---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DocsSidebar from "../../components/DocsSidebar.astro";
---
<Layout title="Rate limits · flipagent docs">
	<div class="cmw cmw-bordered">
		<div class="docs-shell">
			<DocsSidebar />
			<article class="docs-content">
				<h1>Rate limits</h1>
				<p class="lead">Credits cover the work that runs on flipagent's infrastructure — sourcing scrape (1) and AI evaluation (50). Calls that pass through to your own connected eBay account are unmetered. Cached responses don't count. Free is a one-time grant; paid tiers refill monthly (UTC).</p>

				<h2>Tier table</h2>
				<table class="api">
					<thead><tr><th>Tier</th><th>Credits</th><th>Refill</th><th>Burst (min / hour)</th></tr></thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td>Free</td><td>500</td><td>One-time (lifetime grant)</td><td>10 / 200</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Hobby ($19/mo)</td><td>3,000</td><td>Monthly</td><td>30 / 1,200</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Standard ($99/mo)</td><td>100,000</td><td>Monthly</td><td>120 / 6,000</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Growth ($399/mo)</td><td>500,000</td><td>Monthly</td><td>600 / 25,000</td></tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>

				<h2>Credits per call</h2>
				<table class="api">
					<thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Endpoint prefix</th><th>Credits</th></tr></thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr><td>Marketplace data</td><td><code>/v1/items</code>, <code>/v1/categories</code>, <code>/v1/products</code>, <code>/v1/trends</code></td><td>1</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Evaluate</td><td><code>/v1/evaluate</code></td><td>50</td></tr>
						<tr><td>Cache hit</td><td>any (response carries <code>X-Flipagent-From-Cache: true</code>)</td><td>0</td></tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
				<p>Free routes (uncounted, burst rate-limit only): everything that runs on your own connected eBay account or browser — <code>/v1/listings</code>, <code>/v1/sales</code>, <code>/v1/payouts</code>, <code>/v1/transactions</code>, <code>/v1/transfers</code>, <code>/v1/disputes</code>, <code>/v1/policies</code>, <code>/v1/violations</code>, <code>/v1/recommendations</code>, <code>/v1/marketplaces</code>, <code>/v1/me/seller</code>, <code>/v1/messages</code>, <code>/v1/offers</code>, <code>/v1/feedback</code>, <code>/v1/promotions</code>, <code>/v1/markdowns</code>, <code>/v1/ads</code>, <code>/v1/store</code>, <code>/v1/analytics</code>, <code>/v1/feeds</code>, <code>/v1/bids</code>, <code>/v1/translate</code>, <code>/v1/labels</code>, <code>/v1/purchases</code>, <code>/v1/forwarder/*</code>, <code>/v1/ship/*</code>, <code>/v1/expenses/*</code>, <code>/v1/browser/*</code>, <code>/v1/bridge/*</code>, <code>/v1/watching</code>, <code>/v1/saved-searches</code>, <code>/v1/charities</code>, <code>/v1/media</code>, <code>/v1/featured</code>, <code>/v1/listing-groups</code>, <code>/v1/locations</code>, <code>/v1/notifications</code>, <code>/v1/webhooks</code> — plus account routes: <code>/v1/health</code>, <code>/v1/me/*</code>, <code>/v1/keys/*</code>, <code>/v1/connect/*</code>, <code>/v1/billing/*</code>, <code>/v1/takedown</code>, <code>/v1/capabilities</code>, <code>/v1/admin/*</code>.</p>

				<h2>Headers on every authed response</h2>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`X-RateLimit-Limit:              500       # tier credit budget
X-RateLimit-Remaining:          427       # credits left this month
X-RateLimit-Reset:              2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z
X-Flipagent-Credits-Charged:    1         # what this call cost (0 for free routes)
X-Flipagent-From-Cache:         true      # only on cache hits; not charged`}</code></pre></div>

				<h2>Hitting the limit</h2>
				<p>When you've spent your monthly budget, you'll get a <code>429</code>:</p>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`{
  "error": "credits_exceeded",
  "message": "Monthly credit budget for tier \\"hobby\\" is 3000; you've used 3000.",
  "creditsUsed": 3000,
  "creditsLimit": 3000,
  "resetAt": "2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "upgrade": "https://flipagent.dev/pricing"
}`}</code></pre></div>
				<p>If you spike too fast — e.g. 200 calls in one minute on a Hobby key — you'll get a separate <code>429</code> for the burst window:</p>
				<div class="code"><pre><code>{`{
  "error": "burst_rate_limited",
  "window": "minute",
  "message": "Burst rate limit hit (per-minute). Slow down or upgrade for higher limits."
}`}</code></pre></div>
				<p>Paid plan counters reset at <code>00:00 UTC</code> on the first of the next month. The Free tier's 500 credits are a one-time grant — once spent, a maxed-out Free key can only proceed by upgrading. <code>resetAt</code> is <code>null</code> for Free; an ISO timestamp for paid tiers. Hit <code>POST /v1/billing/checkout</code> with <code>tier: "hobby"</code>, <code>"standard"</code>, or <code>"growth"</code> to upgrade.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
